main event: A UFO sighting was reported near Misawa Air Base in Japan on September 14, 1960, observed using ground radar for 2 minutes.
interesting points: The object traveled in a straight course for 2 minutes at a speed of over 900 knots,The object appeared at a heading of 85 degrees, 15 miles southeast of Misawa AB,The nature of the object was considered possibly astronomical, possibly an aircraft or satellite,There was insufficient data for a conclusive evaluation,Multiple reports indicate an unusual lighting in the sky at Misawa AB.
sighted object: unknown aerial object detected by radar
